Abstraction :-
-------------------
==> Abstraction is a key concept in object-oriented programming(OOPS) Concept that allows you to focus on the essential details and 
	ignore the non-essential details
	
==> In java, Abstraction can be achieved by Using abstract class and interfaces.

==> Example : WhatsApp - User1 - msg - Send - User2
			  SBI Bank - Login
			  
			  						Types of Abstraction
			  						--------------------
			  								|
			  			-----------------------------------------
			  			|										|			
			  		(1) 0 to 100%							(2) 100%
			  		-------------							-------------
			  		abstract class							interface(Pure Abstraction)
			  		

	// Abstraction 
	class A
	{
		1) Dm's
		
		2) Methods
			1) abstract method
				ex.. public abstract void test1();
			
			2) non-abstract method
				ex.. public void test2()
					 {
				
					 }
					 		
		3) Constructor
	}
			  		
